    <item>
      <title>新加坡房价放缓，市场降温，租金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/singapore-home-price-growth-slows-rents-fall-in-cooling-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政府采取措施抑制房地产繁荣之后，新加坡私人住宅价格涨幅低于预期，租金在第二季度小幅下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/singapore-home-price-growth-slows-rents-fall-in-cooling-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 00:41:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元“疯狂”涨势可能最早下周就破灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/-crazy-yen-rally-is-at-risk-of-shattering-as-soon-as-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近几周，投资者纷纷买入日元，押注利率最终将向有利于日本的方向倾斜。他们最早将在周三面临关键时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/-crazy-yen-rally-is-at-risk-of-shattering-as-soon-as-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 00:24:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电加入全球科技股暴跌行列，台风过后恢复交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/tsmc-set-to-join-global-tech-rout-after-typhoon-trading-break</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对人工智能的前景感到失望，台湾半导体制造股份有限公司股价在台湾股市恢复交易后，出现三个月来最大跌幅，并加入到全球科技股暴跌的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/tsmc-set-to-join-global-tech-rout-after-typhoon-trading-break</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 00:06:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市跟随美国期货走高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员在美国经济的弹性与未来几个月美联储降息的坚定预期之间取得平衡，股市显示出复苏迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
